<title>ạlq ʿly ạlrb hmk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ạlqi ʿly̱ ạlrb hmk .. fhw yʿwlk)2
 1- ʿndmạ ygẖsẖạk lyluⁿ .. kl mạ fyh ẓlạm
 ygẖdw dẖạ ạllyl mnyraⁿạ .. bḍyạʾ rb ạlslạm
 rbk mw̉ty ạlạ̉gẖạny .. ḥty̱ fy wsṭ ạlậlạm
 ybdl ạlḥzn bfrḥiⁿ .. tẖạbtiⁿ ʿly̱ ạldwạm
 2- fhw lm ysẖfq ʿly̱ ạbnh .. bl bdẖlh llfdạʾ
 hkdẖạ ạllh ạ̉ḥbk .. mạnḥaⁿạ lh ạlrjạʾ
 kyf ạ̉yḍaⁿạ lạ yhbk .. wqt ḍyqk ạlʿzạʾ
 kyf lạ yḥnw ʿlyk .. rạfʿaⁿạ fwq ạlʿnạʾ
 3- fạtkl ʿlyh dwmaⁿạ .. wạtẖqaⁿạ fy wʿdh
 mtẖl ṭfliⁿ ystryḥ .. qlbk fy ḥḍnh
 fhw lm yns rḍyʿaⁿạ .. qd nsy mn ạ̉mh
 fạljạ̉n ạ̹lyh tḥyạ .. ậmnaⁿạ fy strh</lyrics>
</song>